last_episode_to_air.name: Till We Meet Again
last_episode_to_air.overview: In the series finale Nancy plans to leave the clinic to offer services in a third-world country. Things get complicated for Clint when he wrestles with whether to propose to Nancy, or head back to Montana to take over Harley's practice with Sarah. Raul faces a crisis of his own when he learns he has diabetes. Also Mrs. Doss learns she is pregnant and wants to name the baby after Clint or Nancy. This episode features scenes from various episodes of the series as Clint sings " Friends are friends forever. "

name: Doc
overview: Doc is a medical drama/family drama with strong Christian undertones starring Billy Ray Cyrus as Dr. Clint "Doc" Cassidy, a Montana doctor who takes a job in a New York City medical clinic. It ran from March 11, 2001 to November 28, 2004 on PAX. Although set in New York City, all the episodes were shot in and around Toronto, Ontario, Canada.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: A cowboy-boot wearing, ranching, country doctor, who makes house calls, is lured to a sprawling metropolis by a slick lady friend and immediately finds himself neck deep in culture shock. He begins work at a downtown medical clinic and within a day turns the clinic's administrative and medical procedures topsy-turvy.
